<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Our Team - Greymatter Accountancy</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/styles.css">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Sora:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header', { rootPath: '../', currentPage: 'page' }) %>

  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Meet Our Team</h1>
      <p>Experienced professionals dedicated to your success</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Team Members -->
  <section class="team-page">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="team-member-detail">
        <div class="member-avatar-large">SO</div>
        <h2>Sarah Okonkwo</h2>
        <p class="member-role">Managing Director, FCCA</p>
        <p class="member-bio">
          Sarah founded Greymatter Accountancy with a vision to bring intelligent, responsive accounting to London's growing businesses. With 15+ years in practice, she has led audit teams for companies ranging from ambitious startups to established City firms. Her expertise spans financial reporting, audit strategy, and commercial advisory for growth-stage businesses.
        </p>
        <div class="member-expertise">
          <h3>Expertise:</h3>
          <span class="expertise-tag">Financial Reporting</span>
          <span class="expertise-tag">Audit Strategy</span>
          <span class="expertise-tag">Business Advisory</span>
          <span class="expertise-tag">Fundraising Support</span>
          <span class="expertise-tag">FCCA Member</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="team-member-detail">
        <div class="member-avatar-large">JV</div>
        <h2>James Varghese</h2>
        <p class="member-role">Audit & Assurance Lead</p>
        <p class="member-bio">
          James brings Big 4 experience to Greymatter's audit practice. After 8 years at a leading audit firm, he joined to focus on mid-market and growth clients where his expertise could make a real difference. He specializes in complex audit structures, internal controls evaluation, and working with high-growth companies navigating scale.
        </p>
        <div class="member-expertise">
          <h3>Expertise:</h3>
          <span class="expertise-tag">Statutory Audit</span>
          <span class="expertise-tag">Internal Controls</span>
          <span class="expertise-tag">Complex Structures</span>
          <span class="expertise-tag">ISA (UK) Standards</span>
          <span class="expertise-tag">FCA Compliance</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="team-member-detail">
        <div class="member-avatar-large">ER</div>
        <h2>Elena Rossi</h2>
        <p class="member-role">Tax & Compliance Specialist, CTA</p>
        <p class="member-bio">
          Elena is our tax strategist, bringing CTA qualification and deep expertise in UK tax planning. She's helped 100+ clients optimize their tax position, from startup R&D relief strategies to complex corporation tax restructuring. Elena stays ahead of HMRC rule changes and actively advises clients on tax-efficient structures.
        </p>
        <div class="member-expertise">
          <h3>Expertise:</h3>
          <span class="expertise-tag">Corporation Tax</span>
          <span class="expertise-tag">R&D Relief</span>
          <span class="expertise-tag">VAT Strategy</span>
          <span class="expertise-tag">Tax Planning</span>
          <span class="expertise-tag">CTA Qualified</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Supporting Team -->
  <section class="supporting-team">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Supporting Team</h2>
      <p>Beyond our partners, we have a dedicated team of senior bookkeepers, tax consultants, and audit associates supporting our clients daily.</p>
      <div class="team-stats">
        <div class="stat-card">
          <h3>8+</h3>
          <p>Senior Associates</p>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <h3>500+</h3>
          <p>Active Clients</p>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <h3>£50M+</h3>
          <p>Managed Annually</p>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <h3>15+</h3>
          <p>Years Experience</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Culture Section -->
  <section class="team-culture">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Our Culture</h2>
      <p>We believe great accounting comes from great people working in an environment that values:</p>
      <div class="culture-values">
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3><i class="fas fa-handshake"></i> Collaboration</h3>
          <p>We work together, sharing expertise and supporting each client with our full team's knowledge.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3><i class="fas fa-graduation-cap"></i> Continuous Learning</h3>
          <p>Tax and accounting constantly evolve. We invest in professional development and stay ahead of changes.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3><i class="fas fa-user-heart"></i> Client Focus</h3>
          <p>Every decision is made with our clients' success in mind. Your goals are our goals.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3><i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i> Innovation</h3>
          <p>We embrace technology, automation, and better processes to serve you more effectively.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Ready to Work with Our Team?</h2>
      <p>Let's connect with the right specialist for your accounting needs.</p>
      <a href="../index.html#contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get in Touch</a>
    </div>
  </section>
  <%- include('partials/footer', { rootPath: '../', currentPage: 'page' }) %>
</body>
</html>
